                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted in June</hi>, 1865, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">One of the Jurors stated that he</hi>
